The paper discusses the integration of symbolic and connectionist approaches in AI, which is a common topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks (cs.LG) and workflows (cs.SE) in the proposed hybrid representation. Additionally, the paper discusses the representation of knowledge and concepts (cs.CL) and the integration between different processors (cs.SY).
